« i-mentor @ isb | session 2
i-venture @ isb’s women of innovation program aims to provide acceleration support to women-founded/co-founded start-ups by handholding entrepreneurs through their scaling-up journey.
the accelerator is designed to focus on leveraging isb’s strong network to enable women to scale their products/services. women entrepreneurs can then glide through to the go-to-market stage and work on scaling up through focused guidance, workshops, shared learning, and networking along with a platform for fundraising with extensive business growth opportunities.
our i-win (women of innovation) 2.0 accelerator program, wraps up on a high note with an intense demo day that brought 14 investors and the cohort together, engaging them in 1-on-1 pitching over 80+ in-person meetings.

web3 wednesdays – monthly edition
april 12, 2023 
« knowledge series (i-venture @ isb) | episode-2
knowledge series (i-venture @ isb) | episode-3 »
web3 enthusiasts and entrepreneurs in and around, step in for an unmissable evening of learning at the 3rd monthly edition “web3 in india – navigating the ecosystem” of #web3wednesdays (w3w) powered by metabuild.
bringing enthusiasts, builders, entrepreneurs, professionals, and early-stage investors under one roof for a high-intensity dose of industry insights and cross-learning opportunities.
let’s experience an ambitious, community-driven platform that brings web3 to the masses, exploring its opportunities, challenges, use cases, and impact.
